Utility classes available to developers for common tasks.

## Clearfix

`.u-clearfix`

Clear the current element so it always appears on a new line. Can also use the clearfix mixin – `@include clearfix()` in your CSS.

{{#>demo-block }}
<span class="u-clearfix">Lorem</span>
<span>Ipsum</span>
{{/demo-block }}

