## Display Utilities

`.is-hidden,`
`.no-js .is-hidden--noJS`
`.is-shown,`
`.no-js .is-shown--noJS`

Hide/Show from both screenreaders and browsers

{{#>demo-block }}
<span class="is-hidden">Lorem</span>
<span>Ipsum</span>
{{/demo-block }}

`.is-visuallyHidden,`

Hide only visually, but have it available for screenreaders

{{#>demo-block }}
<span class="is-visuallyHidden">Lorem</span>
<span>Ipsum</span>
{{/demo-block }}

`&.focusable:active,`
`&.focusable:focus`

Extends the `.is-visuallyhidden` class to allow the element to be focusable when navigated to via the keyboard

{{#>demo-block }}
